{"tid":835210,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"無人想玩情侶手機攝影班？","createTime":"2018-09-24T16:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T03:07:37.000Z","uid":80658,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cac7b9921284d1b49c4562f642c7dece4c66f842","tid":835210,"uid":80658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:54:19.000Z","msg":"以前拍拖每次女朋友叫我揸電話幫佢影相都好大壓力，基本上無一次影完係滿意，到底係因為女人難服侍，定我真係手殘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我相信好多巴打絲打都面對同樣問題，點解我女朋友咁多要求？點解我男朋友影張相都咁揸ga？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢家NGO推出咗個情侶手機攝影班比大家玩下學下<br />\n覺得彼此間無乜溝通而又周不時因為影相而嘈交都可以報名，完全免費，有導師有小禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n時間<br />\n27/9（四） 19:00-21:00 &amp; <br />\n29/9（六） 12:00-14:00<br />\n有興趣而情侶（24歲或以下）兩節都出席到既可以留tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢一兩日會覆返巴絲打"},{"pid":"f3746445fad788d9186909c56a7743b876e38c8b","tid":835210,"uid":4772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T02:50:59.000Z","msg":"HeHe ok?"},{"pid":"730fc6a1f8ad7b84e0d75d4e76955975765dea97","tid":835210,"uid":104383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T02:55:30.000Z","msg":"年齡限制真苛刻"},{"pid":"1c714960cff3e60dd0f5f334900d3629bd3eaf89","tid":835210,"uid":177288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T03:00:13.000Z","msg":"24以下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b5cce69fcf9917aafe5eec422afa50c9955c0d","tid":835210,"uid":53798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T03:01:29.000Z","msg":"點解有年齡限制? 60歲唔得?"},{"pid":"9239495ca118eb69ebc66b97ab84c6a7a6994dab","tid":835210,"uid":80658,"like":0,"dislike"